text: I propose you not skip the first 57 seconds. There was obviously a lot of planning that went into that.

Yeah ok, I thought I'd seen something like this. Are there drawbacks to these types of services/tools? Or is it usually pretty accurate to what you need it to spit out?
The interesting thing is that I've seen a lot tools that target the "let's get content from PSD/Sketch" out of those files without those apps market.
My only conclusion is that more designers are coding now a days and the market for those tools is growing.
